ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Title: ABA Atlas Services
ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Abstract: ABA Atlas Services provide access to data available from the Allen Brain Atlas resource.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Describe Atlas SRS
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Describes the principal Atlas SRSs (Spatial Reference Systems) supported by this server.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Describe Transformation
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Describes the transformation supported by this server.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Get 2D Images by POI
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Get 2D images at a POI (point of interest) specified in the request.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Get Correlation Map by POI
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Get correlation map at a POI (point of interest) specified in the request.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Get Genes by POI
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Get genes at a POI (point of interest) specified in the request.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Get Structure Names by POI
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Get structure names at a POI (point of interest) specified in the request.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Get Transformation Chain
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Get the chain of transformations required to transform coordinates from and to the given input and output SRS (Spatial Reference System) names.

wps:Process.ows:Title: List SRS Names
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: List the SRSs (Spatial Reference Systems) supported at this server.

wps:Process.ows:Title: List Transformations
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: List coordinate transformations available at this server.

wps:Process.ows:Title: Retrieve 2D Image
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: This function gets a URI reference to a 2D image based on the source URI provided and "cropped" based on the specified lower left (xmin, ymin) and upper right (xmax, ymax).

wps:Process.ows:Title: Transform POI
wps:Process.ows:Abstract: Transform a POI (point of interest) from one SRS (Spatial Reference System) to another.
